snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Ed Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Ed, the psycho-powered bad boy of boxing (with a heart), is almost ready to show you he's the true high-def picture of strength.

Owners of the Deluxe and Ultimate Edition or the Year 1 Character Pass and Ultimate Pass of Street Fighter 6 will obtain Ed when he releases this February.

Official Website:
https://streetfighter.com/6/

Buckler's Boot Camp:
https://www.streetfighter.com/6/buckler/en
